Pune has a beautiful vibe of celebration and togetherness,  thanks to its amazing delicacies that go perfectly well with whisky. What adds sparkle to the celebration is a glass of the most amazing @sterling.reserve B7, that’s made from Scotch malts aged in charred oak barrels. The best part is, it's now available in the youthful city of Pune. Go try it with some authentic Puneri snacks!
